# Mixed-form .nomx sample — exercises every declaration surface
# in one file: record + choice + block-define (with body) + two
# sentence-form to-oneliners. Proves the outer-body terminator
# from 95f9bdc cleanly switches between block bodies and
# sentence-form decls.

record counter holds:
    value is number.

choice status is one of:
    ready.
    running.
    done.

define step that takes c and returns next:
    next is value plus one.
    ensure next is at_least value.

to reset a counter, respond with zero.

to show a counter, respond with its value as text.
